1. *Nestali* su se sa lica zemlje. (They vanished from the face of the Earth.)
2. Njihovu sreću je *nestala* kad su se rastali. (Their happiness had vanished when they parted.)
3. Čovek je iznenada *nestao*. (The man suddenly disappeared.)
4. *Nestaju* svi njegovi strahovi. (All his fears are disappearing.)
5. *Nestalo* je nade da će se situacija promeniti. (Hope had vanished that the situation would change.)
6. Sve što je postojalo je *nestalo*. (Everything that existed had vanished.)